Section 9: Nikki Shakal & Visual Flow (App ki Pehchan)
1. The Logo Glow (Status Indicator)
Shakal: App ka Mono (Logo) screen ke darmiyan mein hoga.
Flow: Jab system scan kar raha ho ya internet se jur raha ho, toh logo ke gird aik halki Blue Glow (roshni) ghumegi. Agar system "Fortress Mode" (Security) mein hai, toh glow Gold ho jayegi.
Emerald Shine: Kaam mukammal hone par logo aik halki si Sabz (Green) chamak dega jo "Tasdeeq" (Success) ki nishani hogi.
2. The Supreme Gold Frame (Authority)
Shakal: Jab bhi Holy Book ka reference ya koi "Divine Command" aayegi, screen ke charon taraf ek bareek Gold Border (Frame) namudar hoga.
Flow: Yeh frame batai ga ke ye maloomat dunya ki sabse unchi sanad se aa rahi hai. Is doran baqi screen halki "Dim" ho jayegi taake focus sirf ilm par rahe.
3. The Task Cards (Simple & Clean)
Shakal: Projects aur Sabaq (Courses) ke liye Rectangle Cards honge.
Detail: Card par koi tasveer nahi hogi, sirf "Subject Name", "Status" (Active/Complete), aur aik chhota sa Progress Bar hoga.
Action: Card ko swipe karne par wo "Open" nahi hoga balki "Expand" (phail) jayega, taake user ko ehsas ho ke wo ek hi system ke andar hai.
4. The "Blue Pulse" (Teamwork Invitation)
Shakal: Jab koi dost teamwork ke liye bulayega, screen par aik halki Blue Pulse (leher) uthegi.
Flow: Yeh pulse shor nahi karegi balki sanjidgi se user ki tawajjo hasil karegi. Accept karte hi dono users ka workspace "Merge" ho jayega.
5. The Virtualization Link (Shadow-Link Face)
Shakal: Jab saste mobile par WhatsApp ya YouTube chal raha hoga, toh screen ke top par ek chhota sa Cloud Icon nazar aayega.
Maqsad: Yeh icon user ko batayega ke uske mobile par bojh nahi hai, balki system server se taqat le raha hai.
6. The 7 Gems Dashboard (Agent Control)
Shakal: 7 chhote Circular Icons (Gems) ek circle mein honge.
Flow: Jis Agent (Gem) ko user touch karega, wo agent darmiyan mein aa kar user se uski boli mein baat shuru kar dega. Inka database delete karne ke liye "Long Press" (daba kar rakhna) ka option hoga.
7. Adab Frame (Distraction Free)
Shakal: Jab user sabaq parh raha ho, toh screen ke corners par "Adab Corners" ban jayenge jo notification bars aur doosri apps ko "Hide" (chupa) denge.
Technical Summary for Notebook:
"Interface ka har element (Button, Card, Glow) Non-Visual hoga. Rang sirf teen honge: Gold (Authority), Blue (Connectivity), aur Emerald Green (Success). Koi bhi cheez 'Blowing' (flashy) nahi hogi taake professional standard barqarar rahe."
Bhai, yeh details aapke developer ko batayengi ke app ki "Rooh" (Soul) kaisi hai.
